channel.title: [PI] Finding dupes and cheats on my server
channel.description: How would I find out if I had any working dupes on my server. I think all of my code is okay but I'm not sure. Anyone know a list of fixed for all of the possible PI dupes? Or if you know how to fix a few reply the fixes. I need to make sure there is no dupes so that I can go ahead and make the gold exchange ticket so people can have a lot of gold. Thx in advance (:

item.title: [PI] Finding dupes and cheats on my server
item.dc:creator: @demps2k9 demps2k9
item.description:
@demps2k9 wrote:

Search untradeable in item.java and itemHandler.java until you find a list of items that are untradeable. Or search the firecape id in those 2 files which is 6570.

The two most common dupes for PI is the Cheat client dupe and the noted item banking dupe.

Read full topic
